SlotEvent.name: SlotEvent
SlotEvent.description: An indication of events occuring in slot

SlotModuleType.name: SlotModuleType
SlotModuleType.description: Type of module present in the slot.

slotTempTable.name: slotTempTable
slotTempTable.description: Table of slots on the device.

slotTempEntry.name: slotTempEntry
slotTempEntry.description: An entry in the slot table. Rows cannot be created or deleted.

slotTempIndex.name: slotTempIndex
slotTempIndex.description: Index into the slot table, starting with 1.

slotName.name: slotName
slotName.description: String description of the name of slot.

slotModuleName.name: slotModuleName
slotModuleName.description: String description of the type of module in slot.

slotModuleSerialNum.name: slotModuleSerialNum
slotModuleSerialNum.description: String description of the serial number of the module in the slot.

slotModuleType.name: slotModuleType
slotModuleType.description: Type of module present in the slot. This is applicable mainly for the newer devices like 6100 and above, which have multiple I/O slots. For older systems like 5100 which don't have slots, the module type would be the device model number.

tptSlotDeviceID.name: tptSlotDeviceID
tptSlotDeviceID.description: The unique identifier of the device sending this notification.

tptSlotID.name: tptSlotID
tptSlotID.description: The slot index which is sending this notification.

tptSlotEvent.name: tptSlotEvent
tptSlotEvent.description: The event occuring in the slot which is sending this notification.

tptSlotChangeNotify.name: tptSlotChangeNotify
tptSlotChangeNotify.description: Notification: Module was inserted on this device
